                        <interp inst="t18431211-name-300" type="given" value="MARGARET"></interp>MARGARET DERBY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of George James Derby. This calico and shift are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431211-name-301" type="witnessName">
