                        <interp inst="t18431211-name-301" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY TAYLOR</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I found this calico at the bottom of the box—the shift was in pawn.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had taken these things, but the shift was my own; the calico was in my box; my mother is now willing to receive me at home.</p>
